			<description><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> </span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Location:</span> At your school <span style="font-weight: bold;">(ignore the location on this job listing - they made us put it in!)</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Hours:</span> 0-20 hours per week, with most hours during beginning and end of school semesters/quarters</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Pay:</span> $12/hour plus performance bonus</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Description:</span>  </p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;">Our website makes it easy for college students to save money on textbooks. We've already saved students tens of thousands of dollars at a few schools, and we need your help to bring the savings to many more schools, including yours!</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;">As Campus Marketing Manager you'll be responsible for helping your fellow students find out about and use the website. We'll give you the training and tools you need to succeed, and plenty of responsibility (which will look great on your resume!). </p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;">You'll be paid well for your time, and if you are particularly successful at marketing, you'll get a bonus that could more than double your hourly earnings! </p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;">Most of the work for this position will occur during the first and last 1-2 weeks of each academic semester/quarter. You may be working 20+ hours per week during those times. You'll have fun working with us, and your classmates will love you - after all, you'll be the one telling them how they can easily save lots of money on their textbooks.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">We are currently in "stealth mode" so we can't tell you who we are or show you the website yet. However, if we'd like to interview you, we'll let you in on the secret before we talk. </span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Responsibilities:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">Ensure as many students as possible know about, and utilize, our textbook shopping website</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">Recruit, hire, train, manage, and motivate up to 20 other students to help market this great, money-saving service to the students at your school</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">Identify and evaluate marketing opportunities on your campus, and make marketing recommendations to company headquarters</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qualifications:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">Excellent marketer and manager - you have some sort of prior experience marketing a service/product and/or managing other people</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">Comfortable in front of people - you have some public speaking experience, theater arts or drama training, Toastmasters experience, or are otherwise in your element when you are addressing a crowd</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">Organized and efficient - you are able to handle multiple responsibilities simultaneously, and are able to prioritize effectively so you spend most of your time doing the things that will make the most difference</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">Socially connected - you have lots of friends on Facebook, you know lots of people on campus, and you find it easy to meet new people</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">How to Apply:</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;">Please visit <a href="http://confidential.theresumator.com/apply" target="_blank">http://confidential.theresumator.com/apply</a>/ to apply for this position. You'll need to submit a resume and answer a few questions, but we've made it as painless as possible. We'll get back to you, but please be patient! Don't worry - we WILL get in touch eventually with everyone that applies. </p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal normal 12px/normal Helvetica;">If you have friends at your school or at other schools that are interested in applying for this position, or might like to help get the word out about our service, please have them visit our jobs page at <a href="http://confidential.theresumator.com/apply/" target="_blank">http://confidential.theresumator.com/apply/</a></p>
